{#-
  Error-401 — "Authentication required" page (Ring 3 S3.1c).

  Composes:
    - _error-shell (sub-template, default variant) for the centered viewport layout
    - Empty (Ring 1, size=lg, h1 title) for illustration + title + body + actions
    - Icon `user` (Ring 1, Lucide curated 30-set substitute — per OQ-57b S2.8 Sidebar
      precedent, no curated-set amend ADR triggered ; substituts retained over
      ADR-0016 to avoid 3rd doctrine-shift in 11 sessions)
    - Button (Ring 1) for the primary + secondary CTAs

  No Stimulus controller — pure server-rendered static page (S3.1c doctrine carry
  from OQ-55). The consumer wraps the kit's pattern in their /401 route handler.

  See `docs/specs/ring3/Error-404.md` §1 for the shared Errors family doctrine
  (composition, anti-enumeration N/A, microcopy verbatim 12-microcopy §"Pages" +
  §"Messages d'erreur", a11y `<main>` landmark + h1 + Empty region).
-#}

{%- set title         = title         | default('theme.error.401.title'|trans) -%}
{%- set body          = body          | default('theme.error.401.body'|trans) -%}
{%- set primaryLabel  = primaryLabel  | default('theme.error.401.primary-cta'|trans) -%}
{%- set primaryHref   = primaryHref   | default('/login') -%}
{%- set secondaryLabel = secondaryLabel | default('theme.error.401.secondary-cta'|trans) -%}
{%- set secondaryHref = secondaryHref | default('/register') -%}
{%- set htmlId        = htmlId        | default('cremona-error-401') -%}
{%- set className     = className     | default('') -%}

{%- set _classes = ['cremona-error-401'] -%}
{%- if className -%}{%- set _classes = _classes | merge([className]) -%}{%- endif -%}

{% embed '@cremona/components/_error-shell/_error-shell.html.twig' with {
  variant: 'default',
  htmlId: htmlId,
  className: _classes | join(' '),
} %}
  {% block content %}
    {% embed '@cremona/components/empty/empty.html.twig' with {
      size: 'lg',
      titleLevel: 'h1',
      icon: 'user',
      title: title,
      body: body,
      htmlId: htmlId ~ '-empty',
    } %}
      {% block actions %}
        {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
          label: primaryLabel,
          variant: 'primary',
          size: 'md',
          href: primaryHref,
        } %}
        {% if secondaryHref %}
          {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
            label: secondaryLabel,
            variant: 'ghost',
            size: 'md',
            href: secondaryHref,
          } %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endblock %}
    {% endembed %}
  {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
